a
\int ^{\infty}_0 \frac{1}{1+2ax+x^2} dx 
\int ^{\infty}_0 \frac{1}{1+2ax+x^2} dx=\int_0^\infty\frac{1}{(x+a)^2+1-a^2}
a=1
a \gt 1
\int_0^\infty\frac{1}{(x+a)^2-(\sqrt{a^2-1})^2}
a \lt 1
\int_0^\infty\frac{1}{(x+a)^2+(\sqrt{1-a^2})^2}
0\leq a<1
x=-a+\sqrt{1-a^2}\tan t
a>1
x=-a+\sqrt{a^2-1}\coth t
\displaystyle \frac{\operatorname{arccosh} a}{\sqrt{a^2-1}}
\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-a^2}}\int_{\arctan\frac{a}{\sqrt{1-a^2}}}^{\pi/2} dt= \frac{\arccos a}{\sqrt{1-a^2}}.
